Was a farmer with wife/child.
Conscripted into Rulon army.
While away, his village was attacked by a Half-Orc.
His wife was assaulted (attempted rape), stabbed Half-Orc in balls.
Wife wounded, escaped with child (Laura).
Sheltered by Willowbottom, where wife died.
Half-Orc tracked 'em to Willowbottom, killed daughter.
Lukas deserted when he heard of the attack on his village.
Returned home to find chaos, searched until he found Willowbottom.
Found his wife's grave & his daughter's body.
Claimed a white blood-stained ribbon from daughter's hair.
Lukas fled to Duvia since he's a Rulon-deserter now.
